nodes.text: Brantis Mo Fresk was a male pilot who owned the starship Vorantis. In the year 7 ABY, he participated in the Karee Blockade Clutch where he beat the starship Brightfox. Sometime later when the smugglers Lando Calrissian and Han Solo visited Frander's Bay in search of a pilot, a barker hollered Fresk's name into one of Solo's ears.
